name: hmdA-Cozy room walk to NEU/Ruggles

description:
cozy room in 2 room 1 bath in a brick 3 floor building, minimum furnishing. 5 min walk to Northeastern University, orange line Ruggles station. Ct1, Ct2 bus to longwood medical area. 1st floor unit. Just a few steps to climb from street.

private room, shared bath/kitchen, living room
